  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this clinical study is to verify the long term effecacy and safety of a
      bilateral deep brain stimulation (DBS) produced by Beijing PINS Medical Co., Ltd. as a
      treatment option for patients with obesity.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
